{{Difficulty|Easy|20px}} <span id="Easy">[[Easy]]</span> is the easiest [[difficulty]] in '''EToH'''. It is represented with a lime green triangle. [[Towers]] in this difficulty can usually be passed on the first try with minimal effort. In this difficulty, the user will mostly encounter basic jumps and rarely a substantially hard obstacle.

Obstacles in this difficulty are commonly found in their simplest formations, with little to no twists or special challenges. Traps are also either labeled with symbols (i.e., conveyors) or not present at all. Obstacles that pose a challenge in towers of this difficulty are forgiving, with safety nets to protect the user from falling.

There are currently 14 [[tower]]s, 4 [[steeple]]s and 4 [[Mini Tower]]s assigned to this difficulty. There are also two removed towers of this difficulty, which are [[Tower of One Equals Zero]] and [[Tower of Another Beginning]]. [[Tower of Slight Inconvenience]], [[Tower of Pleasant Descents]], [[Steeple of Overgrowth]],[[Steeple of Nightfall]], and [[Tower of Various Pressures]] were originally in <span id="Easy">[[Easy]]</span> difficulty, but [[Tower of Slight Inconvenience]] and [[Tower of Pleasant Descents]] got moved to [[Difficult|<span id="Difficult">'''Difficult'''</span>]] and [[Steeple of Overgrowth]], [[Steeple of Nightfall]], and [[Tower of Various Pressures]] got moved to [[Medium|<span id="Medium">'''Medium'''</span>]]. [[Tower of Inception]] and [[Tower of Leaning Ledges]] were also <span id="Easy">[[Easy]]</span> difficulty but as a joke.
