*Although [[Tower of Modernistic Design Choices]] was located within the non-canon area [[Pit of Misery]], it was considered to be canon because it awarded a badge and a [[Tower Point]] before it was removed.  
*[[Ring 1]] has the most <span id="Easy">[[Easy]]</span> [[Towers]] out of any [[Realm]], having 3 <span id="Easy">[[Easy]]</span> [[Towers|towers of any type]]. 
**However, it will be dethroned by [[Ring 0]], which has 5 <span id="Easy">[[Easy]]</span> towers of any type.
*There are only 11 canon Realms with this difficulty.
**[[Silent Abyss]], [[Ring 5]], [[Lost River]], [[Ring 6]], [[Ashen Towerworks]], [[Ring 7]], [[Ring 8]], [[The Starlit Archives]], [[Ring 9]], [[Zone 2]], [[Arcane Area]], [[Zone 5]], [[Zone 6]], [[Zone 7]], [[Zone 8]], [[Zone 9]] and [[Zone 10]] are the only realms without a single <span id="Easy">Easy</span> tower. 
